'''天主教馬普托總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Maputensis}}；{{lang-pt|Arquidiocese de Maputo}}）是[[莫桑比克|莫桑比克]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教省[[總教區|總教區]]，下轄兩個教區。此總教區是該國三個總教區之一。

1612年1月21日設宗座署理區，1783年升為自治監督區。1941年9月4日升為總教區。<ref>{{cite journal
|journal=[[宗座公報|宗座公報]]
|publisher=梵蒂岡出版社
|date=1941年
|volume=33
|title=''Sollemnibus Conventionibus''
|page=14
|url=http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2033%20%5B1941%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf
|access-date=2013-06-09
|archive-date=2020-02-02
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202150801/http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2033%20%5B1941%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>1976年9月18日易名至今。

總教區包括首都[[馬普托|馬普托]]和[[馬普托省|馬普托省]]，2004年有教友675,000人（佔轄區總人口17.5%）、四十個堂區、八十名司鐸。現任總主教為{{link-en|方濟各·希莫尤|Francisco Chimoio}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 22.02.2003 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2003/02/22/0094/00281.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723173455/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2003/02/22/0094/00281.html |archivedate=2019-07-23 |language=it |date=2003-02-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-de|安多尼·茹利亞塞·費雷拉-桑德拉莫|António Juliasse Ferreira Sandramo}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 07.12.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/12/07/181207c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723171550/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/12/07/181207c.html |archivedate=2019-07-23 |language=en |date=2018-12-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為[[亞歷山大·若瑟·桑托斯|亞歷山大·若瑟·桑托斯]]<ref>{{cite web |title=SANTOS Card. Alexandre José Mária dos, O.F.M. |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_santos-dos_ajm.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723172654/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_santos-dos_ajm.html |archivedate=2019-07-23 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

